<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Inventory List</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-links">
        <form action="/auth/sign-out" method="POST">
            <button type="submit" class="link">Log Out</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/items" class="link">View All Items</a>
        <a href="/items/new" class="link">Add New Item</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div>
                <h1 class="title">Inventory managment Tool</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">currently logged in as <%=user.username%></p>
            </div>
        </div>
            <p class="subtitle">A list of stuff</p>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Getting started</h2>
            
            <div class="info-text">
                <p><strong>View all items</strong> - Browse your complete inventory with details</p>
                <p><strong>Add new items</strong> - Track new belongings with categories and locations</p>
                <p><strong>Update items</strong> - Edit details like last seen location or fragile status</p>
                <p><strong>Delete items</strong> - Remove items you no longer need to track</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Notable Features</h3>
            <div class="info-text">
                <p>Track item name, weight, size, and category</p>
                <p>Mark items as daily use or fragile</p>
                <p>Record last seen location for easy finding</p>
                <p>Click any item to view full details</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>